      <title>日元下跌使日本央行加息时机的决定变得复杂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-14/yen-s-fall-complicates-boj-s-decision-on-timing-of-rate-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元兑美元汇率迅速跌破150，这给日本央行带来了进一步的复杂性，因为日本央行认为这是自2007年以来首次加息的最佳时机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-14/yen-s-fall-complicates-boj-s-decision-on-timing-of-rate-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 03:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
